@node SOUNDS "Kąą Sounds"
Kąą Plays sounds on certain events.

Tip :
Its a good idea to assign SOUNDS: to all your sounds dirs
(with assign sounds: [dir] add) and then copy the Kąą
sounds to a directory where they dont show up often.

All the soundfiles are given a pattern so that they will
sit at the bottom of your dir lists,and so that they can
be filtered out by a files-requester.

Here is the list of sounds used by Kąą and the file names:

Event        Soundfile
-----        -----------
DCC Autoget  _K11Autoget.snd
DCC Complete _K11DCC_Done.snd
Display log  _K11EndLog.snd


To change the samples,just copy whatever sound you like over
one of those.
@endnode
