@node MATCHNICK "MatchNick Interface"

The matchnick interface is used all through Kąą nick dependant commands.
You can now use a pattern instead of a nick and it will be replaced with
the real nick.
So you can now use /xdcc send Ari* 1
and the nick will be internally replaced with Ariel.
Or use /xdcc send @ 1
and the @ will be replaced with the nick selected in the channel nicks
list.
@endnode
